<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 2863/75 of the Commission of 3 November 1975 amending Regulation (EEC) No 1105/68 on detailed rules for granting aid for skimmed milk for use as feed </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 2863/75, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1105/68 s&ouml;&ouml;dana kasutatavale l&otilde;ssile toetuse andmise &uuml;ksikasjalike eeskirjade kohta </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> 3. november 1975 EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 (1) of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 740/75 (2), and in particular Article 10 (3) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 740/75, eriti selle artikli 10 l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the second subparagraph of Article 10 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 804/68, in the version at present in force, provides that buttermilk for use as feed shall be regarded as skimmed milk for the purposes of granting aid; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: praegu kehtiva m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 artikli 10 l&otilde;ike 1 teises l&otilde;igus on s&auml;testatud, et toetuste andmisel v&otilde;rdsustatakse s&ouml;&ouml;dana kasutatav petipiim l&otilde;ssiga; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, since that provision came into force, it has become apparent that the present provisions of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1105/68 (3) of 27 July 1968 on detailed rules for granting aid for skimmed milk for use as feed, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2114/75 (4), do not take into account the case of dairies which use the skimmed milk and/or buttermilk which they produce for feeding their own animals; whereas those provisions should therefore be supplemented by certain special rules; </inglise>
<eesti> p&auml;rast k&otilde;nealuse s&auml;tte j&otilde;ustumist on selgunud, et komisjoni 27. juuli 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1105/68 (s&ouml;&ouml;dana kasutatavale l&otilde;ssile toetuse andmise &uuml;ksikasjalike eeskirjade kohta), viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2114/75, praegu kehtivates s&auml;tetes ei v&otilde;eta arvesse meiereisid, mis kasutavad oma loomadele s&ouml;&ouml;daks toodetud l&otilde;ssi ja/v&otilde;i petipiima; seep&auml;rast tuleks neile s&auml;tetele lisada teatavad erieeskirjad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Milk and Milk Products, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The following Article 5a shall be inserted in Regulation (EEC) No 1105/68: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;rusele (EM&Uuml;) nr 1105/68 lisatakse artikkel 5a: </eesti>
<inglise> "Article 5a </inglise>
<eesti> "Artikkel 5a </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a dairy uses solely for feeding its own animals the skimmed milk which it produces, this shall be regarded as a case coming within Article 2 (1) (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 986/68. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui meierei kasutab loomas&ouml;&ouml;dana ainult oma toodetud l&otilde;ssi, kohaldatakse m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 986/68 artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti b. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Such a dairy may receive aid: (a) only for those quantities of skimmed milk which the dairy has declared in writing to the competent agency as being used for feeding its own animals, and </inglise>
<eesti> Sellisele meiereile v&otilde;ib toetust anda: a) ainult selle l&otilde;ssikoguse eest, mille kohta meierei on p&auml;devale ametiasutusele kirjalikult teatanud, et seda kasutatakse oma loomade s&ouml;&ouml;dana </eesti>
<inglise> (b) only if it keeps the monthly record referred to in Article 5. </inglise>
<eesti> b) ainult siis, kui ta peab artiklis 5 osutatud igakuist registrit. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> However, if, in the case described in paragraph 1, only buttermilk is used, the dairy shall receive, for each kilogramme of butter produced and sold, the aid payable for 2.2 kilogrammes of skimmed milk. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud juhul kasutatakse ainult petipiima, antakse meiereile iga toodetud ja m&uuml;&uuml;dud v&otilde;ikilogrammi eest toetust, mis v&otilde;rdub toetusega 2,2 kilogrammile l&otilde;ssile. </eesti>
<inglise> The monthly record referred to in Article 5 (1) shall also contain details of the quantities of butter produced and sold, supported in particular by delivery vouchers and invoices." </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud igakuine register sisaldab ka andmeid toodetud ning m&uuml;&uuml;dud v&otilde;ikoguste kohta, millele on eelk&otilde;ige lisatud saatelehed ja arved." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a dairy concerned so requests, it shall apply with effect from 1 April 1975. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevat m&auml;&auml;rust kohaldatakse alates 1. aprillist 1975 asjaomase meierei taotluse korral. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 3 November 1975. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 3. november 1975 </eesti>
<inglise> For the Commission P.J. LARDINOIS Member of the Commission </inglise>
